### 创建订单
POST http://localhost:8000/orders/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item_id": "item1",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 根据ID获取订单
GET http://localhost:8000/orders/order_1

### 支付订单
POST http://localhost:8000/orders/order_1/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "order_1",
  "amount": 100.0
}

### 检查库存
GET http://localhost:8000/inventory/item1